          "date": "2014-03-24 22:12:57.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-4690 lod: separate master object with master stripe",
        "message": "LU-4690 lod: separate master object with master stripe\n\nSeparate master stripe with master object, so\n1. stripeEA only exists on master object.\n2. sub-stripe object will be inserted into master object\nas sub-directory, and it can get the master object by \"..\".\n\nBy this, it will remove those specilities for stripe0 in\nLMV and LOD. And also simplify LFSCK, i.e. consistency check\nwould be easier.\n\nThis will also clear the iterate API on MDS stack, i.e. LOD\nwill only iterate the whole stripe for master object, otherwise\nit will iterate the single stripe.\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I62d46b53a23eea247e7747bc035b7ad98d79bcf1\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
